---
import Head from '../components/Head.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../config'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import hero from '../../public/about.jpg'
---

<html lang="en">
    <Head title={`About / ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Sound Designer, Music Producer and Composer based in Łódź, Poland." />
    <body>
        <section class="main-wrapper">
            <Header />
            <main>
                <div class="about">
                    <div class="hero-img">
                        <Image
                            src={hero}
                            width={720}
                            alt="Łukasz Brandeburg"
                            quality={90}
                            loading="eager"
                            fetchpriority="high"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <section class="info-wrapper">
                        <div class="name">Hi, I'm Łukasz, also known as "Ceptre"</div>
                        <div class="desc">
                            <div>
                                Games pulled me into sound in 2014, and I've never quite recovered
                                from that first realisation of how much audio shapes what we feel
                                without us knowing why.
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                Before I touch a single tool, I go to understand what a project tells - its tensions, the atmosphere it lives in, what it's afraid of. The emotional logic of a scene comes first.<br> Sound follows.
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                I draw inspiration from nature, reference physics for accuracy, and
                                work with our auditory perception - how sound operates below our
                                consciousness. <br>I often layer elements the listener won't notice
                                but will absolutely feel: human voices buried in textures, frequencies
                                that reach somewhere quieter and deeper.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <div class="desc-below">
                        <div>
                            12+ years in <i>IDM, Tech DnB and Ambient</i> gave me a technical foundation I quietly rely on. It also drew me toward the edges - sounds that don't quite exist yet feel inevitable, like something the ear always knew was there.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <hr>
                <div>
                    <div class="achievements">
                        <div class="col">
                            <div>Lead Sound Designer on several AAA titles.</div>
                            <div title="by MoonshineDNB">Booked internationally as a DJ.</div>
                            <div>Released multiple electronic sample packs.</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col">
                            <div title="SINFUL MAZE, STUDIO, dtdnb">Signed with highly reputable music labels.</div>
                            <div>Regular appearances on Noisia's Vision Radio.</div>
                            <div>Nominated for Best Polish Drum & Bass Track, 2024.</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
            <Footer />
        </section>
    </body>
</html>

<style>
    main {
        align-content: space-evenly;
        max-width: 45rem;
        margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .about {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto auto;
        gap: var(--size-900);
        row-gap: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-img     { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 1; }
    .info-wrapper { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 1; }

    .desc-below {
        grid-column: 1;
        grid-row: 3;
    }

    .desc-below > * + * {
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .achievements {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--size-900);
        color: var(--cl-grey-800);
    }

    .achievements .col {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--size-500);
    }

    .info-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .name {
        color: var(--cl-grey-800);
    }

    .desc > * + * {
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 60rem) {
        .about {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            max-width: 20rem;
            margin-inline: auto;
        }

        .hero-img, .info-wrapper, .desc-below {
            grid-column: unset;
            grid-row: unset;
        }

        .achievements {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        img {
            width: 320px;
        }
    }
</style>